<section id="overview">
  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>The <code>data-bubble</code> attribute provides a full taxonomy of chat bubble shapes for messaging UIs. Each variant has a distinctive tail direction, background color, and alignment built from CSS <code>shape()</code> paths.</p>

  <p>Bubbles are designed to be used inside a flex column container. Each variant sets its own <code>align-self</code> for correct left/right/center positioning.</p>
</section>

